                            <comment id="17477366" author="graben" created="Mon, 17 Jan 2022 18:58:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sure, have a look into  &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13038954/13038954_camel-bridge.zip&quot; title=&quot;camel-bridge.zip attached to CAMEL-17504&quot;&gt;camel-bridge.zip&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. It still works with latest 3.7.x release but fails on 3.14.0. As you can see it polls multiple failure messages which are &quot;skipped&quot; by ErrorHandler and further processed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
